[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0113","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0113.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0045","title":"Apache/NCSA/Netscape Web服务器 nph-test-cgi脚本任意文件列表漏洞","description":"Apache 1.1、NCSA HTTPd 1.5.2 及 Netscape Server 1.12/1.1/2.0 等早期 Web 服务器默认安装的 nph-test-cgi 脚本未对用户请求进行充分过滤，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向该脚本发送特制请求，遍历并列出服务器上的任意文件目录，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响多个主流 Web 服务器早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商建议移除 nph-test-cgi 脚本或升级至不受影响版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0045"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.793","remediation":"立即删除或禁用 nph-test-cgi 脚本（该脚本仅用于测试，不应部署在生产环境）；升级 Apache 至 2.4 及以上版本（1.3 系列已终止支持，1.1 含多个安全漏洞）；如使用 NCSA HTTPd，建议迁移至 Apache 2.4；Netscape Enterprise Server 用户应升级至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 7.0+；同时在 Web 服务器配置中禁止 CGI 目录执行任意文件读取操作，严格控制 CGI 脚本文件权限为 750。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0045","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19536","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0045","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0045.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0045.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7h3-hmx5-3w4r/GHSA-h7h3-hmx5-3w4r.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0045.yaml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0045.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0113.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0113.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0113.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0232","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0232.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0101","title":"IBM AIX/Microsoft Windows/Sun SunOS gethostbyname() 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x/4.x、Windows 95/98/2000/NT 4.0 及 SunOS 5 等操作系统的 `gethostbyname()` 库函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送恶意的 DNS 主机名解析请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个主流操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，对核心服务器和网络设备危害极大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0101"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.340","remediation":"受影响系统均已停止安全技术支持，建议立即升级至厂商仍在支持的最新操作系统版本。AIX 用户应升级至 AIX 7.2 及以上；Solaris 用户升级至 Solaris 11.4；Windows 平台已无法通过官方补丁修复，须迁移至 Windows 10/11 或 Server 2016+。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或 DNS 服务器上过滤恶意 DNS 响应数据包，限制应用程序对 gethostbyname() 的输入长度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-13.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22251","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0101.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0101","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/doodad-labs/threat-intelligence/blob/ee308632cd35c3a8b60a89f181457ce4fae96eed/data/exploits/CVE-1999-0101.22251.sh","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0101.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/README.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q9f-93v8-w2pf/GHSA-2q9f-93v8-w2pf.json","https://github.com/kylekirkby/Python-Exploit-Search-Tool/blob/8e84b77a6ff689ce32d04884f9ea75de04ae0433/platforms/multiple/remote/22251.sh","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0232.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0232.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0226","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0226.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0096","title":"Sendmail decode 别名远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 的 decode 别名功能存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标 Sendmail 服务器发送特制邮件，利用 decode 别名将邮件内容通过管道传递给程序处理，从而覆盖系统敏感文件或执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 发行版及使用 Sendmail 的系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0096"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1996-12-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"移除或注释 Sendmail aliases 文件中的 decode 别名条目（通常在 /etc/aliases 或 /etc/mail/aliases）；升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 及以上版本（该版本默认移除了 decode 别名）；若无升级条件，在 sendmail.cf 中限制 decode 别名的使用范围并禁用邮件管道传递至程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/122&type=0&nav=sec.sba"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0226.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0120","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0120.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0043","title":"INN innd 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"INN (InterNetNews) 新闻服务器守护进程 innd 1.5 版本存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的 \"newgroup\" 和 \"rmgroup\" 等控制消息，在消息中注入 shell 元字符，从而在目标服务器上以 innd 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 INN 1.5 的 Unix 类系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0043"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-12-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.437","remediation":"立即升级 INN (InterNetNews) 至 1.6 或更高版本，该版本修复了控制消息 (newgroup/rmgroup) 中 shell 元字符注入问题。如无法升级，可在 innd.conf 中禁用控制消息处理 (e.g., `allownewgroups: false`、`allowrmgroups: false`)，并在防火墙层面限制对 NNTP 端口 (119/tcp) 的访问，仅允许可信来源连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0043"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0120.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0110","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0110.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0044","title":"SGI IRIX fsdump 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 操作系统中 fsdump 命令存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于 fsdump 在处理敏感文件时未能正确限制普通用户的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过修改系统敏感文件将自身权限提升为 root 超级用户，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0044"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.660","remediation":"升级至 SGI IRIX 6.3 及以上版本以修复 fsdump 权限提升漏洞。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/fsdump` 移除 fsdump 的 setuid 位，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限运行；同时通过 `chmod 700 /usr/sbin/fsdump` 限制仅 root 用户可执行，防止本地用户提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19280","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0044","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0044.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0044.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1211931-bc17-4b72-a817-dc1a2d02bd86.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0110.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0278","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0278.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0129","title":"Sendmail Sendmail .forward 和 :include: 文件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sendmail 在处理 .forward 或 :include: 配置文件时存在权限校验缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的配置文件写入任意文件，从而获取目标系统的组权限。该漏洞在默认配置下即可触发，攻击者无需特殊权限。影响 BSD 系列操作系统及使用 Sendmail 的其他 Unix 类系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0129"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-12-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:39.183","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.8.4 或更高版本，该版本禁止使用全局可写的 .forward 和 :include: 文件。确保用户主目录及 .forward 文件的权限设置为 755 和 644 或更严格，:include: 引用的文件不得为其他用户可写。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中添加 O DontBlameSendmail=forwardfilegroupwritable,includeifgroupwritable 等安全限制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1996-25.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0278.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0135","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0135.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0050","title":"HP HP-UX newgrp 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.20 系统中的 `newgrp` 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞进行提权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0050"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.550","remediation":"建议立即为 HP-UX 10.20 安装 HP 官方补丁 PHCO_13542（或更高版本的累积补丁束），替换存在溢出缺陷的 newgrp 程序。若暂时无法打补丁，可通过命令 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/newgrp` 移除该程序的 setuid 位作为临时缓解，并限制普通用户访问，同时加强审计日志监控对 newgrp 的异常调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0050","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19535","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0050","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0050.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f29h-343h-g8gj/GHSA-f29h-343h-g8gj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0050.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--89a6ac85-e7f6-4f7a-9588-810221d536e3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0135.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0279","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0279.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0130","title":"Sendmail 守护进程本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sendmail 在处理守护进程模式启动时存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于 Sendmail 二进制文件设置了 setuid root 权限，本地攻击者可以通过启动 Sendmail 守护进程模式，利用其与 setuid 相关的缺陷获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 BSD 2、Sendmail 8.x、FreeBSD 2.1.x、HP-UX 10.x、AIX 4、RedHat 4 等多个 Unix 系操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0130"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:39.340","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，该版本重构了 daemon 模式权限检查，禁止普通用户以 root 权限启动 daemon。各受影响操作系统（BSD/FreeBSD/HP-UX/AIX/RedHat）厂商均已发布对应安全补丁，可联系厂商获取。临时缓解措施：移除 sendmail 二进制文件的 setuid root 位（`chmod u-s /usr/sbin/sendmail`），但会影响正常邮件投递功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/716","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19556","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0130.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0130","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0130.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0130.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-01xx/CVE-1999-0130.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0279.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0554","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0554.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0336","title":"HP HP-UX mstm 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 mstm 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 mstm 程序发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，成功利用后可获取系统的 root 最高权限。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需身份认证即可从本地利用，完全控制受影响系统，影响 HP-UX 多个版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0336"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.723","remediation":"立即从 HP Support Portal 获取并安装对应 HP-UX 版本的 mstm 安全补丁（搜索 HP-UX Security Bulletin 相关条目）。如无法打补丁，可执行 `chmod 500 /usr/bin/mstm` 移除 setuid root 权限，阻止普通用户通过该二进制提权；同时通过文件权限将 mstm 执行权限限制为仅 root 用户，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0336"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0554.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0518","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0518.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0311","title":"HP-UX fpkg2swpk 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 fpkg2swpk 工具存在权限提升漏洞，本地普通用户可利用该工具未正确处理权限的缺陷，通过执行特定操作获取 root 权限。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的 HP-UX 系统，执行任意操作。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0311"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1996-11-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 至 11.0 及以上版本，或安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9612-042 中对应的补丁。如无法升级，可移除 fpkg2swpk 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/fpkg2swpk）并限制可执行用户组，阻断本地提权路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0311","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9612-042"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0518.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0463","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0463.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0277","title":"Sun Solaris WorkMan 任意文件覆盖本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 WorkMan 日历程序存在任意文件覆盖漏洞。本地攻击者可利用 WorkMan 程序的缺陷，通过符号链接攻击或直接指定路径覆盖系统任意文件（如 /etc/passwd 或 /bin/su 等），从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地用户账号才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。通过覆盖关键系统文件实现提权，目前厂商已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0277"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-10-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.473","remediation":"立即移除 WorkMan 二进制文件的 setuid 权限：执行 `chmod -s /usr/bin/workman`。如已安装 Sun 补丁 100176-01（适用于 Solaris 2.4/2.5/2.5.1），请安装该补丁修复符号链接竞争条件。若业务不需要该日历程序，建议直接删除 `/usr/bin/workman` 以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0277"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0463.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0094","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0032","title":"BSD系统 lpr 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统的 lpr 打印服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向带 -C（分类）选项的 lpr 命令传入超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1.5、NeXTstep 4.x、IRIX 6.4、SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.4 等基于 BSD 的系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0032"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.833","remediation":"建议将系统升级至已修复该漏洞的版本（FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、BSD/OS 3.0 及以上、IRIX 6.5 及以上），或应用厂商补丁替换存在缓冲区溢出的 lpr 二进制。如无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr）限制本地普通用户提权，或改用 cups-lpr 等现代打印系统替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-042.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/707"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0187","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0187.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0075","title":"Washington University wu-ftpd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 守护进程在处理 PASV 命令时存在缺陷，已通过身份认证的攻击者向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 QUOTE PASV 命令后，可触发 ftpd 进程产生核心转储（core dump），造成敏感内存信息泄露或导致服务拒绝。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd 服务，攻击者需先获取有效的登录凭据才能利用此漏洞，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0075"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.340","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5 或更高版本以修复 PASV 命令处理缺陷；如无法升级，在 /etc/ftpaccess 中设置 passive off 禁用 PASV 模式作为临时缓解。由于 wu-ftpd 已停止维护，建议长期迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在维护的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/5742"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0187.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0419","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0419.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0234","title":"GNU Bash 命令分隔符注入漏洞","description":"Bash 在处理命令解析时存在分隔符逻辑缺陷，会将字节值 255（0xFF）错误识别为命令分隔符。攻击者通过向 Bash 执行的字符串中注入包含 0xFF 字节的特制数据，可导致命令注入，实现以当前用户权限执行任意命令，造成机密性、完整性、可用性部分损失。该漏洞影响 openlinux 等使用早期 Bash（1.x 及以前版本）的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0234"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.140","remediation":"立即升级 Bash 至 2.0 或更高版本，255 字节在已修复版本中不会被解析为命令分隔符。如无法升级，可对用户输入进行严格过滤，移除或替换 ASCII 255 字节（0xFF），并限制不可信数据传入交互式 Bash 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0234"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0419.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0391","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0391.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0206","title":"Sendmail 8.8.0 MIME 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"sendmail 8.8.0 及 8.8.1 版本在处理 MIME 邮件消息时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制的 MIME 格式邮件触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，最终获取 root 权限。受影响的 sendmail 版本被广泛部署于各类 Unix/Linux 系统中，危害极大，CVSS 评分为 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0206"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.607","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.8.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 8.8.2 中修复。如无法立即升级，可禁用 MIME 解析功能或在邮件网关层面过滤畸形 MIME 消息作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0206"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0391.toml"}]